 required to authenticate it using your mobile app.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How Does The Nexo Card Work?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nexo allows you to borrow fiat money or <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/crypto-academy.org\/what-are-stablecoins\/\">stablecoins<\/a> without a credit check. Rates begin at 0%, and you are not required to sell your cryptocurrency.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A credit line is a term for the amount borrowed. It is possible to borrow between $50 and $2 million. Whenever you make a purchase, you instantly get cash through Nexo\u2019s credit lines with APRs as low as 0%, depending on your loyalty tier. Because there is no minimum monthly payment with the Nexo Card, you may pay it back whenever you like.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)<\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Where Can I Use The Nexo Card?<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The card may be used everywhere in the EEA where Mastercard is accepted.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Is The Nexo Card Worth It?<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Giving Nexo\u2019s cards a try is undoubtedly worth it, especially with rates beginning at 0% and the fact that you will not be required to sell your cryptocurrencies. Furthermore, the Nexo card application process is a breeze.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Takeaways<\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nexo has unveiled its Nexo Card with Mastercard\u2019s help. It lets users use cryptocurrency without selling it.\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For new investors, obtaining this card is a straightforward process.<\/span><\/i><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-